metadata.name: marvallous - VOODOO WARRIORS #1
metadata.description: marvallous - creative collective is revolutionizing the bond between artists and audience! We are driving to give every fan the opportunity to transition from an observer and consumer to a stakeholder in their favorite artist! Investors can vote on career driving decisions of artists, support them on their journey and get rewards with every step to success they take! As the artists career grow, investors profits grow too! Be part of diverse adventures our artists take, assist them on their way to the top and benefit with every success! Support and share royalties with your favourite ones! First drop: Voodoo Warriors collection, main artist: marvallouseve! Spread Peace and Love through music and art!
